<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.8">
<l>kaṉṟataṉāl viḷaveṟintu kaṉiyutirtta kāḷai kāmarucīr mukilvaṇṇaṉ kālikaḷmuṉ kāppāṉ</l>
<l>kuṉṟataṉāl maḻaitaṭuttuk kuṭamāṭu kūttaṉ kulavumiṭaṅ koṭimatiḷkaḷ māḷikaikō puraṅkaḷ</l>
<l>tuṉṟumaṇi maṇṭapaṅkaḷ cālaikaḷtū maṟaiyōr tokkīṇṭit toḻutiyoṭu mikappayiluñ cōlai</l>
<l>yaṉṟalarvāy matuvuṇṭaṅ kaḷimuralu nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">with bannered walls, mansions, gateways,</l>
<l rend="indent">pavilions teeming with jewels, [and] halls,</l>
<l>There where bees hum, having sipped nectar in the day’s [new] buds</l>
<l rend="indent">in the groves where abide pure Vedic experts,</l>
<l rend="indent">gathering in groups so they multiply with [their] assembly,</l>
<l>The place where rejoices the youth who fell woodapple fruit throwing a calf,</l>
<l rend="indent">the cloud-colored one with a desirable nature,</l>
<l>The performer who danced with pots, having blocked the rain with a hill,</l>
<l rend="indent">to protect the herd long ago.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
